          <td colspan="2" valign="top" class="titulo2">Three Poems and After Twenty Years :  Reflections on Exile and Language <span class="texto2">by <a href="http://interlitq.org/staff/carmen_bugan/bio.php" class="link3">Carmen Bugan</a></span></td>
